                   [replace (BOX GLOBALREGION) of INDVELT with (create REGION
                                                                  using X WIDTH _
                                                                        (DIFFERENCE
                                                                         (fetch (POSITION XCOORD)
                                                                            of NEWPOSITION)
                                                                         (fetch (REGION LEFT)
                                                                            of X))
                                                                        HEIGHT _
